title: Peter Frampton - Live In Detroit 1999 DVD - cOOt
description:
Pine Knob amphitheater is the setting for an unforgetable
evening with legendary musician PETER FRAMPTON.
Hold on to your seat as he rocks the house with a fusion
of old favorites, new hits and screaming guitar riffs that
leave the audience breathless. It's Frampton at his
boldest, brightest and very best.


Dolby Digital 5.1
Video Standard NTSC
16.9 widescreen
Runtime 100 Mins.

DVD Bonus Materials Include:

Video Interview With Peter
Biography
Discography
